{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c230b2f613","title":"给续范亭的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"faa9364e7d","index":0,"year":1944,"month":8,"day":22,"articleId":"c230b2f613"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji19.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji19":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ddb38517b9","type":"paragraph","text":"给续范亭的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"c230b2f613"},{"id":"f9fae71c1b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年8月22日）范亭同志：你的检文式的文章（寄闽信）看到，即可发表，并广播出去，廉顽立信”，报奋人心。听王彬同志说才知你已入医院，写此等文章当然会加重你的病。但是听说休养方法已改为静卧，是很好的凯丰同志用此法已愈。江青用此法也好得多了。希望你用此法完全治好。近日国际国内对我们同情的日多，过去被封锁、打击、每骂的孤立状态可能起一大变化。这个消息或者也可帮助你治病。希望坚持卧治政策。敬礼！","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"c230b2f613"},{"id":"ea70c688b5","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"c230b2f613"},{"id":"eba6a78b40","type":"paragraph","text":"八月二十二日1]参见《孟子·万章下》：“故闯伯爽之风者，顾夫廉，夫有立志。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"c230b2f613"}],"page":{"id":"78b5c7f901","publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"c230b2f613","start":87,"end":87}}}},"__N_SSG":true}